HEADWORD: Counter-courant
<hw>Coun"ter-cou*rant"</hw> <pr>(-k??-r?nt")</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<fld>(Her.)</fld> <def>Running in opposite directions; -- said of
animals borne in a coast of arms.</def>⟦br⟧
